        <updateDate>2024-06-14T16:26:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill expands the definition of <em>critical mineral</em> under the Energy Act of 2020 to include copper. Thus, this bill requires the Department of Energy and other agencies to conduct a variety of efforts to ensure a secure and reliable supply chain of copper.&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
